Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.40,0:21:19.25,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Ài, cái đấy... {You know, that's...}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:20.56,0:21:22.26,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Vòng cổ cho chó mà? {a dog collar, right?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.26,0:21:23.42,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Hế?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.42,0:21:25.88,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Sao không nói sớm! Đồ điên! {T-Tell me that before I put it on! You jerk!}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.20,0:21:27.26,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Điên thật mà! {Seriously! Geez!}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.51,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Đi nói với cô Hiratsuka luôn đây! {I'm telling Hiratsuka-sensei on you!}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.41,0:21:32.43,Default - 1080,,0,0,0,,Cảm ơn cái vòng, đồ ngốc. {Thanks, jerk.}
